title: Test Pilot - MetalFunkaPunkeDelic
description:
TEST PILOT METALFUNKAPUNKEDELIC!

Comin in for a Crash Landing Down onto Your hard drive!
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
You may ask

Who is this Test Pilot band?
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

My answer is:

 Test Pilot is a great band from Milwaukee Wisconsin they have a unique fun sound. They infuse Punk, Metal, Funk and Reggae into a great new sound that's sure to get people interested.

One of the best local bands in these parts, and more unique in a time where everyone's busy being emo. 

Test Pilot will uplift you and make you wanna party instead of bleeding your wrists!
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 They did a mini tour in bars and clubs around Milwaukee in 06 and went to the BO-dog battle of the bands and after that they did a small US tour and even made it out to Whiskey a Go Go in cali.

I recently uploaded this but the quality was not as good as these. (192)

If your looking for new music Test Pilot is surely for you

These guys are friends of mine and I love their Music so please give them a listen and please tell your friends!

If you like them Please Seed and show your support for the band on MySpace!
